AddressInfo.Title: IKEA warehouse Bergvik, Karlstad
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
2 charging stations (greep posts) on the parking lot near the main entrance, close to the pick-up road look at the service desk exit. Free parking for IKEA customers, no fee for electricity. Type 2 contact. Sign on station says "Welcome to charge during warehouse opening hours". 
Secondary phone contact is the support number on the charging station.

GeneralComments: 2 stations, total 4 outlets on marked parking lots. More details at https://www.uppladdning.nu/SiteDetail.aspx?id=6aa72bc6-1953-49c0-81ce-c521c33eb830&ln=sv
